{"id":151735,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/高清图片：看看一派谎言的朝鲜政治宣传画/","date":"2011-05-11T19:57:43Z","modified":"2011-05-11T19:57:43Z","title":"高清图片：看看一派谎言的朝鲜政治宣传画","content":"<p><strong>高清图片：看看一派谎言的朝鲜政治宣传画&#8212;-卜荣华</strong></p>\n<p>在一切专制统治下，一切宣传工具都是为了专制统治阶级政权服务的，为了维持他们的不可告人的罪恶统治，他们用大量的以假乱真的谎言欺骗人民，比如在我小时候，就经常信以为真的听广播上和报刊杂志上大量宣传，什么“台湾人民生活在水深火热之中”、“美国人民吃了上顿没下顿”“万恶的旧社会如何如何黑暗”“世界上2/3的人民还生活在水深火热之中”“敌人一天天烂下去，我们一天天好起来”等等，后来，随着改革开放，当谎言不攻自破的时候，才幡然悔悟，原来我们才是世界上最可怜的真正生活在水深火热中的一群人，国民经济都到了崩溃的边缘了，还歌功颂德大唱赞歌，或者自吹自擂自娱自乐的大唱黄粱梦之歌，从这些充满了谎言的朝鲜政治宣传画中，可以看到当年我们曾经经历过的生活的影子&#8212;卜荣华</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.blogchina.com/authorEdit/userimg_01/jiuquan195310/3tvrb74t-1304994186.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.blogchina.com/authorEdit/userimg_01/jiuquan195310/wmzeiky0-1304994169.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.blogchina.com/authorEdit/userimg_01/jiuquan195310/0j28ilfh-1304994144.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.blogchina.com/authorEdit/userimg_01/jiuquan195310/92kt4qzp-1304994121.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.blogchina.com/authorEdit/userimg_01/jiuquan195310/gxr5bji2-1304994094.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.blogchina.com/authorEdit/userimg_01/jiuquan195310/7gxysc4m-1304994075.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.blogchina.com/authorEdit/userimg_01/jiuquan195310/gfy9tmsd-1304994057.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.blogchina.com/authorEdit/userimg_01/jiuquan195310/yrr1vdbt-1304994031.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.blogchina.com/authorEdit/userimg_01/jiuquan195310/22eha0i1-1304994009.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.blogchina.com/authorEdit/userimg_01/jiuquan195310/lesm4wdc-1304993987.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.blogchina.com/authorEdit/userimg_01/jiuquan195310/1athgfkg-1304993969.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.blogchina.com/authorEdit/userimg_01/jiuquan195310/b50nrxoj-1304993952.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><